# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# NEETHIVAAN — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit the real .env to GitHub
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Server ──────────────────────────────────
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# ── MongoDB Atlas ────────────────────────────
# Format: mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/neethivaan
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/neethivaan

# ── JWT ─────────────────────────────────────
# Generate: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(64).toString('hex'))"
JWT_SECRET=your_super_long_random_jwt_secret_here_minimum_32_characters
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your_refresh_token_secret_here
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=30d

# ── Bcrypt ───────────────────────────────────
BCRYPT_SALT_ROUNDS=12

# ── CORS ─────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated list of allowed frontend origins
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

# ── Email (Gmail SMTP) ───────────────────────
# Step 1: Enable 2FA on Gmail
# Step 2: Go to Google Account → Security → App Passwords
# Step 3: Generate App Password for "Mail"
EMAIL_USER=your_gmail@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your_16_char_app_password
EMAIL_FROM=NEETHIVAAN Portal <your_gmail@gmail.com>

# ── Cloudinary (Free tier - file uploads) ────
# Sign up free at https://cloudinary.com
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_api_key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_api_secret

# ── Auto Escalation ───────────────────────────
AUTO_ESCALATE_DAYS=5

# ── Client URL (for password reset emails) ───
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ── Rate Limiting ─────────────────────────────
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX=100
AUTH_RATE_LIMIT_MAX=10
CHATBOT_RATE_LIMIT_MAX=10
